A new Hyundai Motorstudio has opened in Jakarta! Join us and @bts.bighitofficial on the path to the future of mobility and experience our new global brand space in Senayan Park, Indonesia.

The Hyundai Motorstudio exists to connect people to our heritage and future mobility vision. We aim to present clean mobility experiences that emphasize reshaping society and touching people's everyday lives through sustainability. 

#Hyundai #Hyundaimotorstudio #Jakarta #BTS #mobility #cleanmobility #sustainability #HyundaiMotorstudio_SenayanPark

latestPosts.caption:
A pioneering journey in six chapters.

Swipe through our scrapbook and explore Hyundai’s unwavering commitment to hydrogen - from our visionary first step in 1998, to the world’s first mass-produced hydrogen fuel cell vehicle, and now, the all-new NEXO.

Ready for the next chapter?

#Hyundai #Hydrogen #ClearlyCommitted #HyundaiHeritage #NEXO

27 years of believing in hydrogen, 27 years of being #ClearlyCommitted.

Hyundai is shaping a hydrogen-powered future in a rapidly evolving auto industry by drawing from its rich heritage, empowered by the founding spirit and dedication of its visionaries.

#Hyundai #hydrogen #HyundaiHeritage

Do you know how breakthroughs are made?
After 7 years since the first-generation NEXO, we’re proud to introduce the all-new NEXO – the cutting-edge fuel cell electric vehicle featuring a bold new design and enhanced technology.

Clearly Committed, The all-new NEXO.

#Hyundai #NEXO #HyundaiFCEV #FCEV #ClearlyCommitted #HyundaiNEXO #hydrogen #hydrogenmobility

A vision for inspiring mobility experiences: At Hyundai Motor Group, we believe the best user experience goes beyond convenience to inspire. Our newly opened UX Studio Seoul embodies this vision, placing customer voices at the heart of advanced vehicle development.

This collaborative hub integrates your insights directly into the design process, ensuring that every touchpoint enhances your mobility experience.

Join us in shaping the future!

#Hyundai #UXStudioSeoul #FutureMobility #HyundaiInnovation
